  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to lxqt-globalkeys</title>

    <para>
      The <application>lxqt-globalkeys</application> package contains a daemon
      used to register global keyboard shortcuts as well as an editor for
      keyboard shortcuts.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

